value.name: Mark Watson and Mat Ryer's The Company
value.original_name: Mark Watson and Mat Ryer's The Company
value.overview: Cult interactive game born at the Edinburgh festival two years ago. You're on a company awayday to Edinburgh. Your votes decide what happens. You find yourself in some fiendish puzzles. You may have a knife. It is not a cult. Follow @MarkWatsonCo to catch up on the story; new employees welcome.
